OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,FCoronation Street will weave the
OL,7,Fcolour purple, a global symbol for
OL,8,Fdomestic violence awareness,
OL,9,Fthroughout its latest episode to
OL,10,Fhighlight the issue.
OL,12,FThe ITV soap is currently showing Todd
OL,13,FGrimshaw, played by Gareth Pierce, as
OL,14,Fthe victim of months of physical and
OL,15,Femotional abuse at the hands of his
OL,16,Fpartner, Theo Silverton, played by
OL,17,FJames Cartwright.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/9
