OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776276669
OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,FIn the latest instalment of the soap,
OL,7,Fviewers will see Grimshaw finally
OL,8,Freport Silverton to the police after
OL,9,Fenduring a "horrific beating" in a
OL,10,Fstylised episode which uses purple to
OL,11,Fhighlight those impacted by domestic
OL,12,Fabuse.
OL,14,FIn a preview of the episode on
OL,15,FWednesday, 15 April, residents of
OL,16,FWeatherfield including Tyrone Dobbs
OL,17,Fand Lauren Bolton are seen dressed in
OL,18,Fpurple or donning a purple accessory.
OL,26,@qD@LOUqD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
