OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776276669
OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,FDobbs and Bolton, who were both
OL,7,Fvictims in previous domestic abuse
OL,8,Fstorylines on the soap, and other
OL,9,Fcharacters wearing purple will serve
OL,10,Fas a visual reminder of the reality of
OL,11,Fhow many people are impacted by the
OL,12,Fissue.
OL,14,FGrimshaw will also wear the colour `
OL,15,Fwhich represents peace, courage,
OL,16,Fsurvival, and dedication to ending
OL,17,Fabuse ` as he prepares to free himself
OL,18,Ffrom the abusive relationship.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776276669
OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,FProducer Kate Brooks said: "We wanted
OL,7,Fthis episode to illustrate that Todd
OL,8,Fis unfortunately one of many; his
OL,9,Fstory, whilst harrowing, sadly
OL,10,Freflects the lives of so many other
OL,11,Fpeople who are entrenched in abusive
OL,12,Frelationships.
OL,14,F"As powerful and unflinching as this
OL,15,Fepisode is, it also offers a glimpse
OL,16,Finto how there can be hope in the
OL,17,Fdarkest of times, and that there is
OL,18,Fsupport out there to guide and help
OL,19,Fpeople rebuild their lives.
OL,26,@nD@\OUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/9
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776276669
OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,F"Ultimately this is a story about
OL,7,Fsurviving ` and people gaining
OL,8,Fstrength and support from others
OL,9,Fwho've been through similar
OL,10,Fsituations."
OL,12,FPierce, who called the storyline a
OL,13,F"tough watch at times", hailed the
OL,14,Fimportance of highlighting the issue
OL,15,Fon TV and said: "So many domestic
OL,16,Fabuse survivors have shared their
OL,17,Fexperiences with us throughout this
OL,18,Fstoryline.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@LO]uD@AOUuD@VO]wD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/9
