OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776276669
OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,F"Weaving those voices into this
OL,7,Fepisode through the use of colour felt
OL,8,Flike a powerful reminder of how
OL,9,Fwidespread stories like Todd's are."
OL,11,FGalop, an LGBTQ+ anti-abuse charity,
OL,12,Fwas called in by the Coronation Street
OL,13,Fresearch team to ensure the story was
OL,14,Ftold accurately and sensitively.
OL,26,@nD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/9
