FL,398,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776276669
OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,FBen Kernighan, co-chief executive of
OL,7,Fthe charity, said: "For LGBT+ people,
OL,8,Fthere's often an added fear that
OL,9,Fservices won't take their experiences
OL,10,Fseriously or that they will have to
OL,11,Fexplain, defend, or justify parts of
OL,12,Ftheir identity or relationship."
OL,14,FCoronation Street also consulted with
OL,15,FManchester Women's Aid, a charity
OL,16,Fwhich specialises in domestic abuse
OL,17,Fservices, for the ongoing storyline.
OL,26,@oD@TOUtD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/9
