PN,39708
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F397A1776276669
OL,3,CCorrie to use purple to raise
OL,4,Cawareness of domestic abuse
OL,6,FClaire Harris, strategic lead of the
OL,7,Fcharity, said: "This storyline with
OL,8,FTodd has really highlighted the
OL,9,Fcoercive nature of domestic abuse, the
OL,10,Fimpacts it can have in all areas of
OL,11,Fsomeone's life and the barriers and
OL,12,Fchallenges they can face to safely
OL,13,Fleaving.
OL,15,F"No-one should ever have to face this
OL,16,Falone and support is out there."
OL,18,FCoronation Street is available on
OL,19,FITV1, ITVX and Youtube.
OL,26,@oD@POUwD@AOUxD@`O]
